	/**
	 * @description           Creates a list of sObjects
	 * @param sObj            Type of sObjects to create
	 * @param numberOfObjects Integer number of objects to create
	 * @param doInsert         Boolean should this method insert the created object?
	 * @return                `SObject[]`
